  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Adult ventilated patient (Age &gt;18).

          -  The patient or his guardian is able and voluntarily prepared to sign the Informed
             Consent Form.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Known, preexisting DVT or PE.

          -  Patient who is participating in another clinical trial.

          -  Patient with contraindication to use of the device including patients with leg
             gangrene, recent skin graft or medical situations where increase venous and lymphatic
             return is undesirable.
      </textblock>
